Second Department,

September, 1960

(September 8, 1960) The People of the State of New York, Respondent, v. Daniel J. Donovan and John R. Doherty, Appellants.

Motion to enlarge time granted; appellants to perfect the appeal for the December Term; appeal ordered to be placed on the calendar for December 5, 1960. Nolan, P. J., Beldoek, Ughetta, Kleinfeld and Christ, JJ., concur.
